Melt margarine in large saucepan over low heat. Add marshmallows and stir until completely melted. Remove from heat. Add Kellogg's(R) Rice Krispies(R) cereal. Stir until well coated. Using buttered spatula or waxed paper, press mixture evenly into 15 x 10 x 1-inch pan coated with cooking spray. Allow to cool slightly. Using 4-inch star-shaped cookie cutter, cut into star shapes. Decorate as desired using frosting. Use a dot of prepared frosting to attach red cinnamon candies. Best if served the same day.